  "prompt": "How do I get call history for my Airtel prepaid number?",
  "response": "To get call history for your Airtel prepaid number, you can try these methods:\n\n1. Using Airtel My App:\n- Download Airtel My App\n- Login to your account\n- Go to 'Usage Details' or 'Call History'\n\n2. USSD Code Method:\n- Dial *123# from your Airtel number\n- Select option for call details/history\n- Follow on-screen instructions\n\n3. Online Portal:\n- Visit airtel.in\n- Log into your account\n- Check call history section\n\n4. SMS Method:\n- Send SMS \"VH\" to 121\n- Receive call history details on your phone\n\n5. Customer Care:\n- Call 121 (Airtel helpline)\n- Request call history details\n- May require customer verification\n\n6. Visit Airtel Store:\n- Personally visit nearest Airtel store\n- Request printed call history details\n\nNote: Some methods might have charges or limitations on the number of records retrieved. The exact steps might vary slightly depending on your specific plan and region.",
